article.description: — Samkelo Cele had 20 points as Southern topped Alabama A&M 73-57 on Wednesday.
article.headline: Cele scores 20 to carry Southern over Alabama A&M 73-57
article.linkText: Cele scores 20 to carry Southern over Alabama A&M 73-57
article.story: BATON ROUGE, La. -- — Samkelo Cele had 20 points as Southern topped Alabama A&M 73-57 on Wednesday. Jayden Saddler had 19 points and eight assists for Southern (7-8, 7-4 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Kirk Parker added 10 rebounds. Jalen Johnson had 19 points for the Bulldogs (6-5, 4-5). Jevon Tatum added 17 points. The Jaguars evened the season series against the Bulldogs. Alabama A&M defeated Southern 68-58 on Jan. 23. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
